channel.title: Comments on: Beck swoops in and finishes the fight

item.title: By: Eric Greenwood
item.dc:creator: Eric Greenwood
item.description: i've never liked fiery furnaces. and this was just the cherry on top. i'm down with anything from beck, despite the scientology.

item.title: By: Logan K. Young
item.dc:creator: Logan K. Young
item.description: personally, i like some of the stuff the furnaces do. but you're right here, what a fuck up this time. as for beck, i've more or less stopped listening. those velvets covers are the best thing he's done in a long time. and don't get me started on harry partch...overrated masturbatory calculus!
